{"_id": "32691828|None", "id": "32691828", "infons": {}, "passages": [{"infons": {"journal": "J. Infect. Dis.; 2020 Jul 21 . doi:10.1093/infdis/jiaa437", "year": "2020", "type": "title", "authors": "Yamagishi T, Ohnishi M, Matsunaga N, Kakimoto K, Kamiya H, Okamoto K, Suzuki M, Gu Y, Sakaguchi M, Tajima T, Takaya S, Ohmagari N, Takeda M, Matsuyama S, Shirato K, Nao N, Hasegawa H, Kageyama T, Takayama I, Saito S, Wada K, Fujita R, Saito H, Okinaka K, Griffith M, Parry AE, Barnetson B, Leonard J, Wakita T, ", "section": "Title"}, "offset": 0, "text": "Environmental sampling for severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 during COVID-19 outbreak in the Diamond Princess cruise ship.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "3", "infons": {"identifier": "2697049", "type": "Species"}, "text": "severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2", "locations": [{"offset": 27, "length": 47}]}, {"id": "4", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 82, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "5", "infons": {"identifier": "3635", "type": "Gene", "ncbi_homologene": "4046"}, "text": "ship", "locations": [{"offset": 131, "length": 4}]}], "relations": []}, {"infons": {"type": "abstract", "section": "Abstract"}, "offset": 137, "text": "A COVID-19 outbreak occurred in the Diamond Princess cruise ship and we sampled environmental surfaces after passengers and crews vacated the cabins. SARS-CoV-2 RNA was detected from 58 out of 601 samples (10%) from case-cabins 1-17 days after the cabins were vacated, but not from non-case-cabins. There was no difference in the detection proportion between cabins for symptomatic (15%, 28/189, Cq: 29.79-38.86) and asymptomatic cases (21%, 28/131, Cq: 26.21-38.99). No SARS-CoV-2 virus was isolated from any of the samples. Transmission risk of SARS-CoV-2 from symptomatic and asymptomatic patients may be similar and environmental surfaces could be involved in viral transmission.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "12", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 139, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "13", "infons": {"identifier": "3635", "type": "Gene", "ncbi_homologene": "4046"}, "text": "ship", "locations": [{"offset": 197, "length": 4}]}, {"id": "14", "infons": {"identifier": "2697049", "type": "Species"}, "text": "SARS-CoV-2", "locations": [{"offset": 287, "length": 10}]}, {"id": "15", "infons": {"identifier": "2697049", "type": "Species"}, "text": "SARS-CoV-2", "locations": [{"offset": 608, "length": 10}]}, {"id": "16", "infons": {"identifier": "2697049", "type": "Species"}, "text": "SARS-CoV-2", "locations": [{"offset": 684, "length": 10}]}, {"id": "17", "infons": {"identifier": "9606", "type": "Species"}, "text": "patients", "locations": [{"offset": 729, "length": 8}]}], "relations": []}], "relations": [], "pmid": 32691828, "pmcid": null, "created": {"$date": 1595454010467}, "accessions": ["gene@3635", "disease@MESH:C000657245", "species@2697049", "species@9606"], "journal": "J. Infect. Dis.", "year": 2020, "authors": ["Yamagishi T", "Ohnishi M", "Matsunaga N", "Kakimoto K", "Kamiya H", "Okamoto K", "Suzuki M", "Gu Y", "Sakaguchi M", "Tajima T", "Takaya S", "Ohmagari N", "Takeda M", "Matsuyama S", "Shirato K", "Nao N", "Hasegawa H", "Kageyama T", "Takayama I", "Saito S", "Wada K", "Fujita R", "Saito H", "Okinaka K", "Griffith M", "Parry AE", "Barnetson B", "Leonard J", "Wakita T"]}
{"_id": "32691730|None", "id": "32691730", "infons": {}, "passages": [{"infons": {"journal": "Clin. Nephrol.; 2020 Jul 21 . doi:10.5414/CN110164", "year": "2020", "type": "title", "authors": "He H, Liao C, Wang R, Wu T, Zhang J, Hu C, Shui H, ", "section": "Title"}, "offset": 0, "text": "Co-infection with SARS-CoV-2 and parainfluenza virus in a hemodialysis patient: A case report : .", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "3", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D060085", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "Co-infection", "locations": [{"offset": 0, "length": 12}]}, {"id": "4", "infons": {"identifier": "2697049", "type": "Species"}, "text": "SARS-CoV-2", "locations": [{"offset": 18, "length": 10}]}, {"id": "5", "infons": {"identifier": "9606", "type": "Species"}, "text": "patient", "locations": [{"offset": 71, "length": 7}]}], "relations": []}, {"infons": {"type": "abstract", "section": "Abstract"}, "offset": 98, "text": "BACKGROUND: In December 2019, the 2019 novel coronavirus disease (COVID-19) caused by SARS-CoV-2 emerged in China and now has spread to many countries. Limited data are available for hemodialysis patients with COVID-19. CASE PRESENTATION: We report a 66-year-old man with confirmed COVID-19 and parainfluenza virus infection in Wuhan. We describe the clinical characteristics, radiological findings, and treatment of the hemodialysis patient, including the patient's initial pneumonia at presentation with progression to acute respiratory distress syndrome (ARDS). DISCUSSION AND CONCLUSION: Our case underscores the possibility of SARS-CoV-2 co-infection with other pathogens in hemodialysis patients and the importance of early identification of COVID-19.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "21", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "2019 novel coronavirus disease", "locations": [{"offset": 132, "length": 30}]}, {"id": "22", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"o