{"_id": "32690988|None", "id": "32690988", "infons": {}, "passages": [{"infons": {"journal": "Radiol Case Rep; 2020 Sep ; 15 (9) 1646-1649. doi:10.1016/j.radcr.2020.07.009", "year": "2020", "article-id_pmc": "PMC7342008", "type": "title", "authors": "Al Mazrouei SS, Saeed GA, Al Helali AA, Ahmed M, ", "section": "Title"}, "offset": 0, "text": "COVID-19-associated encephalopathy: Neurological manifestation of COVID-19.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "3", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 0, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "4", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D001927", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "encephalopathy", "locations": [{"offset": 20, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "5", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 66, "length": 8}]}], "relations": []}, {"infons": {"type": "abstract", "section": "Abstract"}, "offset": 76, "text": "Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) is a viral disease, also known as severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2, was first reported in Wuhan, China, December 2019. Respiratory manifestations from the induced acute lung injury were the most common reported findings. Few cases showed extrapulmonary manifestations. COVID-19-associated neurological manifestations have not been widely reported. In this report, we describe a case of encephalopathy in a patient with COVID-19 infection.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "16", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "Coronavirus disease 2019", "locations": [{"offset": 76, "length": 24}]}, {"id": "17", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 102, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "18", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D001102", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "viral disease", "locations": [{"offset": 117, "length": 13}]}, {"id": "19", "infons": {"identifier": "2697049", "type": "Species"}, "text": "severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2", "locations": [{"offset": 146, "length": 47}]}, {"id": "20", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D055371", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "acute lung injury", "locations": [{"offset": 290, "length": 17}]}, {"id": "21", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 396, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "22", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D001927", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "encephalopathy", "locations": [{"offset": 513, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "23", "infons": {"identifier": "9606", "type": "Species"}, "text": "patient", "locations": [{"offset": 533, "length": 7}]}, {"id": "24", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 546, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "25", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D007239", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "infection", "locations": [{"offset": 555, "length": 9}]}], "relations": []}], "relations": [], "pmid": 32690988, "pmcid": null, "created": {"$date": 1595454010467}, "accessions": ["disease@MESH:C000657245", "species@9606", "disease@MESH:D055371", "species@2697049", "disease@MESH:D001102", "disease@MESH:D007239", "disease@MESH:D001927"], "journal": "Radiol Case Rep", "year": 2020, "authors": ["Al Mazrouei SS", "Saeed GA", "Al Helali AA", "Ahmed M"]}
{"_id": "32690987|None", "id": "32690987", "infons": {}, "passages": [{"infons": {"journal": "Radiol Case Rep; 2020 Sep ; 15 (9) 1633-1637. doi:10.1016/j.radcr.2020.07.003", "year": "2020", "article-id_pmc": "PMC7340044", "type": "title", "authors": "Husain R, Corcuera-Solano I, Dayan E, Jacobi AH, Huang M, ", "section": "Title"}, "offset": 0, "text": "Rhabdomyolysis as a manifestation of a severe case of COVID-19: A case report.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "2", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D012206", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "Rhabdomyolysis", "locations": [{"offset": 0, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "3", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 54, "length": 8}]}], "relations": []}, {"infons": {"type": "abstract", "section": "Abstract"}, "offset": 79, "text": "Since the outbreak of the ongoing pandemic of the novel coronavirus disease (COVID-19) in Wuhan, China, from December 2019, we have learned that multiple organs can be affected with the potential for various complications. Although myalgia is a frequent symptom in COVID-19 patients, no imaging findings of rhabdomyolysis have been featured in the literature. We report a case of presumed rhabdomyolysis in a 38-year-old male with COVID-19 based on the clinical presentation, laboratory results and radiological findings. By discussing the diagnostic rationale and reviewing the relevant literature we hope to advance the existing understanding of this disease and its effects on the musculoskeletal system.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "12", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "novel coronavirus disease", "locations": [{"offset": 129, "length": 25}]}, {"id": "13", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 156, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "14", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D063806", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "myalgia", "locations": [{"offset": 311, "length": 7}]}, {"id": "15", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 344, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "16", "infons": {"identifier": "9606", "type": "Species"}, "text": "patients", "locations": [{"offset": 353, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "17", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D012206", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "rhabdomyolysis", "locations": [{"offset": 386, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "18", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D012206", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "rhabdomyolysis", "locations": [{"offset": 468, "length": 14}]}, {"id": "19", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 510, "length": 8}]}], "relations": []}], "relations": [], "pmid": 32690987, "pmcid": null, "created": {"$date": 1595454010467}, "accessions": ["species@9606", "disease@MESH:D063806", "disease@MESH:C000657245", "disease@MESH:D012206"], "journal": "Radiol Case Rep", "year": 2020, "authors": ["Husain R", "Corcuera-Solano I", "Dayan E", "Jacobi AH", "Huang M"]}
{"_id": "32690986|None", "id": "32690986", "infons": {}, "passages": [{"infons": {"journal": "Radiol Case Rep; 2020 Sep ; 15 (9) 1629-1632. doi:10.1016/j.radcr.2020.05.059", "year": "2020", "article-id_pmc": "PMC7262528", "type": "title", "authors": "Brown A, Dluzewski S, Malhotra A, ", "section": "Title"}, "offset": 0, "text": "Presumed pulmonary COVID-19 infection detected incidentally on breast MR.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "2", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 19, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "3", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D007239", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "infection", "locations": [{"offset": 28, "length": 9}]}], "relations": []}, {"infons": {"type": "abstract", "section": "Abstract"}, "offset": 74, "text": "COVID-19 is an infectious disease caused by severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2). A global pandemic was declared by the World Health Organization on 11 March 2020. Approximately 30% of infected individuals are asymptomatic. We present the case of a 68-year-old female who underwent outpatient breast magnetic resonance (MR) imaging for assessment of a left breast mass. The study demonstrated abnormal sub-pleural high T2 signal intensity change within in the partially visualised lungs, which showed enhancement following administration of contrast. Concern was raised that the pulmonary changes may represent COVID-19 infection. The patient was urgently contacted and denied any current symptoms but reported suffering mild upper respiratory tract symptoms two weeks earlier. An outpatient chest radiograph demonstrated changes consistent with COVID-19 infection and the patient was treated as COVID-19 positive and advised to self-isolate for 7 days as per Public Health England guidance. Due to increasing breathlessness the patient presented to our emergency department the next day and underwent a CT pulmonary angiogram which demonstrated segmental pulmonary emboli and sub-pleural consolidation in keeping with COVID-19 infection. This represents the first case of COVID-19 identified on breast MR imaging that the authors have seen and highlights the importance of prompt identification and flagging of incidental pulmonary findings to minimise further transmission of the virus in asymptomatic carriers.", "sentences": [], "annotations": [{"id": "23", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 74, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "24", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D003141", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "infectious disease", "locations": [{"offset": 89, "length": 18}]}, {"id": "25", "infons": {"identifier": "2697049", "type": "Species"}, "text": "severe acute respiratory syndrome coronavirus 2", "locations": [{"offset": 118, "length": 47}]}, {"id": "26", "infons": {"identifier": "2697049", "type": "Species"}, "text": "SARS-CoV-2", "locations": [{"offset": 167, "length": 10}]}, {"id": "27", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D007239", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "infected", "locations": [{"offset": 283, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "28", "infons": {"identifier": "9606", "type": "Species"}, "text": "outpatient", "locations": [{"offset": 380, "length": 10}]}, {"id": "29", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 709, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "30", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:D007239", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "infection", "locations": [{"offset": 718, "length": 9}]}, {"id": "31", "infons": {"identifier": "9606", "type": "Species"}, "text": "patient", "locations": [{"offset": 733, "length": 7}]}, {"id": "32", "infons": {"identifier": "9606", "type": "Species"}, "text": "outpatient", "locations": [{"offset": 879, "length": 10}]}, {"id": "33", "infons": {"identifier": "MESH:C000657245", "type": "Disease"}, "text": "COVID-19", "locations": [{"offset": 944, "length": 8}]}, {"id": "34", "infons": {"identifier"